### POST - /auth/register
POST {{BASE_URL}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Jonson Cave",
    "email": "jonson.cave@ex.com",
    "password": "12345678",
    "role": "DONOR"
}


### POST - /auth/login
